text.data-name: Buffet 119K th ga vi 6 mn n c bit ca Lu Nm Thun Vit. Kt hp cng vi nc lu gia truyn ca nh hng, tho thch vi hai la chn v Lu Thi v Lu Ngt. Lu Nm Thun Vit ph hp cho nhiu khch hng vi nhiu la chn v lu khc nhau.
